{
  "texts": [
    "The pseudo label calibration seeks to align pseudo-label estimates with a desired ground truth distribution.",
    "To alter unlabeled samples for creating diverse augmentations, we propose a SoftMix operation that generates both questionand context-side augmentation, not in the input space, but in their representation space.",
    "Our experimental results demonstrate that our proposed model significantly outperforms models of a similar scale and LLM, marking a step forward in domain-specific QA model development.",
    "Our main contributions can be summarized as follows: • We collected ScholarChemQA, a chemical QA dataset for answering research questions.",
    "This benchmark can be used to evaluate the chemistry domain capabilities of AI models."
  ]
}